This is fear, pure and simple - &quot;the little-death that brings total obliteration.&quot;

Blizzard has let its fear of what might happen destroy their ability to manage the game well and make well-reasoned decisions.  There are good reasons for some fears.  And the way to address them is though innovative and intelligent game design choices.  But they haven&#039;t really made any game design choices.  They are following in the footsteps of others, i.e., &#039;being a better Everquest&#039;, and thus are afraid of all the things they perceive as problems in other games.
